            "instructions": "<ol>\r\n<li>I own Arma 3<\/li>\r\n<li>I own a working microphone and Teamspeak 3 is installed in a Push-to-Talk configuration<\/li>\r\n<li>I will ensure my Steam account is set to 'public' for the duration of the application process<\/li>\r\n<li>I am at least 17 years of age<\/li>\r\n<li>I am willing to work as part of a team<\/li>\r\n<li>I will always respect others (both members and the public)<\/li>\r\n<li>I will not bring the name of 3CB into disrepute<\/li>\r\n<li>I can attend operations\/training sessions at least 2-3 hours per week<\/li>\r\n<li>I will complete training within 30 days, to the best of my abilities<\/li>\r\n<li>I will not discuss or share Arma3 addons which the 3CB mod team are testing<\/li>\r\n<li>I have read and agree to the General Rules<\/li>\r\n<\/ol>\r\n\r\nI agree to the above <strong>terms & conditions<\/strong>, and understand that failure to meet these will result in a kick\/ban.",
